                <h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="has-another-government-department-already-done-this"><a href="/knowledge-hub/how-to-get-ai-for-your-project#has-another-government-department-already-done-this" class="govuk-link">1. Has another government department already done this?</a></h2>
                <p class="govuk-body">No, this seems new.</p>
                <h2 class="govuk-heading-l govuk-!-margin-top-7" id="is-this-a-common-need"><a href="/knowledge-hub/how-to-get-ai-for-your-project/is-this-a-common-need#is-this-a-common-need" class="govuk-link">2. Is this a common need?</a></h2>
                <p class="govuk-body">No, this is specialised.</p>
                <h2 class="govuk-heading-l govuk-!-margin-top-7" id="do-your-current-software-tools-already-have-ai-features"><a href="/knowledge-hub/how-to-get-ai-for-your-project/do-your-current-software-tools-already-have-ai-features#do-your-current-software-tools-already-have-ai-features" class="govuk-link">3. Do your current software tools already have AI features that could do this?</a></h2>
                <p class="govuk-body">No, we need something different.</p>
                <h2 class="govuk-heading-l govuk-!-margin-top-7" id="how-should-we-get-this-built"><a href="/knowledge-hub/how-to-get-ai-for-your-project/how-should-we-get-this-built#how-should-we-get-this-built" class="govuk-link">4. How should we get this built?</a></h2>
                <p class="govuk-body">We need a company to build it.</p>
                <h2 class="govuk-heading-l govuk-!-margin-top-9" id="hire-experts">Hire a company to build it</h2>
                <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">How long?</h3>
                <p class="govuk-body">3 - 6 months</p>
                <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Who to involve</h3>
                <p class="govuk-body">Commercial team, tech team, legal team, data protection officer, ethics team.</p>
                <div class="govuk-inset-text">
                    <p class="govuk-body"><span class="govuk-!-font-weight-bold">Faster, more flexible option</span> Competitive Flexible Procedure lets companies test their ideas with you first (through proof-of-concepts) before you commit to the full contract. This reduces risk and ensures you see evidence before deciding.</p>
                </div>
                <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">What you'll need</h3>
                <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                    <li>Business case</li>
                    <li>Clear description of what you need</li>
                    <li>Success criteria (how you'll know it works)</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="govuk-inset-text">
                    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Important contract protections:</h4>
                    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                        <li>You own everything the AI creates (Crown copyright for outputs)</li>
                        <li>You can get your data back if you switch (strong exit clauses)</li>
                        <li>They explain how the AI works (transparency on training data)</li>
                        <li>Clear audit and security standards</li>
                        <li>Detailed Service Level Agreements (SLAs) with penalties</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
